**story**
once upon a time, in a forest, their lived a monkey who resided on a tree whis was on the banks of a river. in the same forest thier lived crocodile and his wife.
one day crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree the kind hearted monkey oferd him some fruet,
the crocodile came bake nexts day for more fruits. as days passed by the crocodile and the monkey became good friends 